Package: loudgain
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: ReplayGain 2.0 loudness normalizer based on the EBU R128/ITU BS.1770 standard
 loudgain is a versatile ReplayGain 2.0 loudness normalizer, based on the
 EBU R128/ITU BS.1770 standard (-18 LUFS) and supports FLAC, Ogg, MP2, MP3, MP4,
 M4A, ALAC, Opus audio files.
 .
 It uses the well-known mp3gain commandline syntax
 but will never modify the actual audio data.
